cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG

The paper focuses on analyzing the temporal patterns from multimedia content of advertisement videos, which involves techniques from multimedia analysis, information retrieval, computer vision, natural language processing, and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.MM (Multimedia), followed by cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.CV (Computer Vision) for analyzing visual components, cs.CL (Computation and Language) for analyzing textual components, and cs.LG (Machine Learning) for the proposed framework.
